title: Feel it! Fully outfitted firefighter shows his dance moves
text:
Volunteer firefighter Darren Vincent participated in a National Night Out event in Enron, Va., and joined the crowd to show off his dance moves.
More popular and trending stories
Fortunately, someone caught it on video and posted it to Chesterfield County Fire and EMS’s Facebook page .
Enon Volunteer Fire Department at National Night Out
Posted by Darren Vincent on Tuesday, August 4, 2015 That dance song, by the way, is more than a few years old. It’s called the Cupid Shuffle.
